{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 434706, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 90143, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "题呢", "timestamp": 1602344678, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 434744, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 90143, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "题呢", "timestamp": 1602345121, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 434813, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 90143, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "先用$E_1$再用$E_2$更新时，由贝叶斯公式\n$P_{E_1} (D|E_2)=\\frac{P_{E_1} (D) P_{E_1} (E_2 | D)}{P_{E_1} (D) P_{E_1} (E_2 | D) + P_{E_1} (D^c) P_{E_1} (E_2 | D^c)}$\n带入以下四式\n    $P_{E_1} (D) = P(D  | E_1) = \\frac{P(D  E_1)}{P(E_1)}$\n    $P_{E_1} (E_2|D) = P(E_2 | DE_1) = \\frac{P(DE_1E_2)}{P(DE_1)}$\n    $P_{E_1} (D ^ c) = P(D ^ c | E_1) = \\frac{P(D ^ c E_1)}{P(E_1)}$\n    $P_{E_1} (E_2|D^ c) = P(E_2 | D^ c E_1) = \\frac{P(D^ c E_1E_2)}{P(D^ c E_1)}$\n可得\n$P_{E_1} (D|E_2)=\\frac{P(DE_1E_2)}{P(DE_1E_2)+P(D^c E_1E_2)}$\n这是轮换对称的，所以\n$P_{E_1} (D|E_2)=P_{E_2} (D|E_1)=P(D|E_1 E_2)$", "timestamp": 1602346079, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 434834, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 90143, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 谢谢！", "timestamp": 1602346256, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 434869, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 90143, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: carol不知道这个推导能不能解释清楚题目的要求，但是这个运算过程应该是没有错的qwq", "timestamp": 1602346580, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 434885, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 90143, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为什么Dave不记得有这道题（害怕", "timestamp": 1602346892, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 90143, "reply": 6, "tag": null, "text": "#做法征集：\n今天晚上初等概率论考试的第9题（Bayes一致性）应该怎么做比